.TH "LIGHTNING-UNLOCK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-unlock \- clightning HSM unlock + secret-store integration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning unlock
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning unlock — clightning HSM unlock + secret-store integration.

Implements FEAT-184. Subcommands:
  (default)    interactive: prompt password, unlock daemon, store in secret
  --stored     non-interactive: pull from secret, unlock
  rotate       change password (daemon + secret store atomic)
  forget       drop the stored secret

Storage:
  secret get lightning.<wallet>.unlock
  <wallet> defaults to 'default'; override with --wallet <name>
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
